    <entry>
      <title>Linux常用命令</title>
      <link href="/2018/11/01/linux%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/"/>
      <url>/2018/11/01/linux%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="查看盘剩余空间大小"><a href="#查看盘剩余空间大小" class="headerlink" title="查看盘剩余空间大小"></a>查看盘剩余空间大小</h3><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">df -h</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><h3 id="按文件size进行排序"><a href="#按文件size进行排序" class="headerlink" title="按文件size进行排序"></a>按文件size进行排序</h3><figure class="highlight stata"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">du -<span class="keyword">sh</span> * | <span class="keyword">sort</span> -rh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="tar压缩与解压缩命令"><a href="#tar压缩与解压缩命令" class="headerlink" title="tar压缩与解压缩命令"></a>tar压缩与解压缩命令</h3><p>tar -cvf 压缩后文件名 需要压缩的文件<br>tar包压缩的时候用cvf参数，解压的时候用xvf参数<br>或压缩的时候用czvf参数，解压的时候用xzvf参数</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -xvf <span class="selector-tag">b</span><span class="selector-class">.tar</span> -C ../</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="查看进程cpu及内存使用率"><a href="#查看进程cpu及内存使用率" class="headerlink" title="查看进程cpu及内存使用率"></a>查看进程cpu及内存使用率</h3><p>ps 如果想查看进程的CPU占用率和内存占用率，可以使用aux 如果想查看进程的<br>父进程ID和完整的COMMAND命令，可以使用ef<br>USER：用户名称<br>PID：进程号<br>%CPU：进程占用CPU的百分比<br>%MEM：进程占用物理内存的百分比<br>VSZ：进程占用的虚拟内存大小（单位：KB）<br>RSS：进程占用的物理内存大小（单位：KB）与%mem对应<br>TT：终端名称（缩写），若为？，则代表此进程与终端无关，因为它们是由系统启动的<br>STAT：进程状态，其中S-睡眠，s-表示该进程是会话的先导进程，N-表示进程拥有比普通优先级更低的优先级，R-正在运行，D-短期等待，Z-僵死进程，T-被跟踪或者被停止等等<br>STARTED：进程的启动时间<br>TIME：CPU时间，即进程使用CPU的总时间<br>COMMAND：启动进程所用的命令和参数，如果过长会被截断显示</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>ps -ef</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>ps aux</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="实时显示进程情况"><a href="#实时显示进程情况" class="headerlink" title="实时显示进程情况"></a>实时显示进程情况</h3><figure class="highlight coq"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">top</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>（up 显示的是系统运行时常）</p><h3 id="查询占用端口"><a href="#查询占用端口" class="headerlink" title="查询占用端口"></a>查询占用端口</h3><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">netstat -anp</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>-a (all)显示所有选项，默认不显示LISTEN相关<br>-t (tcp)仅显示tcp相关选项<br>-u (udp)仅显示udp相关选项 -n 拒绝显示别名，能显示数字的全部转化成数字。-l 仅列出有在 Listen (监听) 的服務状态<br>-p 显示建立相关链接的程序名</p><h3 id="打印空行行号"><a href="#打印空行行号" class="headerlink" title="打印空行行号"></a>打印空行行号</h3><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">awk</span> <span class="string">'/^$/&#123;print NR&#125;'</span> sed.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="计算和"><a href="#计算和" class="headerlink" title="计算和"></a>计算和</h3><figure class="highlight stata"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">cat</span> sed.txt | awk -F <span class="string">" "</span> '&#123;<span class="keyword">sum</span>+=<span class="variable">$2&#125;</span> END &#123;<span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="keyword">sum</span>&#125;'</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="按数字排序求和"><a href="#按数字排序求和" class="headerlink" title="按数字排序求和"></a>按数字排序求和</h3><figure class="highlight stata"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">sort</span> -<span class="keyword">n</span> <span class="keyword">test</span>.txt | awk '&#123;a+=<span class="variable">$0</span>;<span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="variable">$0&#125;</span> END &#123;<span class="keyword">print</span> "<span class="keyword">sum</span>”=a&#125;'</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="替换内容"><a href="#替换内容" class="headerlink" title="替换内容"></a>替换内容</h3><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sed -<span class="selector-tag">i</span> <span class="string">'s/xx/xx/g'</span> filepath</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="历史"><a href="#历史" class="headerlink" title="历史"></a>历史</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">history</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="杀死所有chrome进程"><a href="#杀死所有chrome进程" class="headerlink" title="杀死所有chrome进程"></a>杀死所有chrome进程</h3><figure class="highlight perl"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ps -ef | <span class="keyword">grep</span> chrome | <span class="keyword">grep</span> -v <span class="keyword">grep</span> | awk <span class="string">`&#123;print $2&#125;`</span> | xargs <span class="keyword">kill</span> -<span class="number">9</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="反选文件，移动到上层目录"><a href="#反选文件，移动到上层目录" class="headerlink" title="反选文件，移动到上层目录"></a>反选文件，移动到上层目录</h3><figure class="highlight coq"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ls | <span class="type">grep</span> -v <span class="number">1</span> | <span class="type">mv</span> $(xargs) ../</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="批量改名"><a href="#批量改名" class="headerlink" title="批量改名"></a>批量改名</h3><figure class="highlight coq"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">rename</span> originname replacenme ./*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="找文件名"><a href="#找文件名" class="headerlink" title="找文件名"></a>找文件名</h3><figure class="highlight dos"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">find</span> /<span class="built_in">path</span> -name kewords</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="通过监听端口找进程"><a href="#通过监听端口找进程" class="headerlink" title="通过监听端口找进程"></a>通过监听端口找进程</h3><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">lsof -<span class="selector-tag">i</span>:端口号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="查找jar包是否有类名"><a href="#查找jar包是否有类名" class="headerlink" title="查找jar包是否有类名"></a>查找jar包是否有类名</h3><figure class="highlight gradle"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">grep</span> fullname .<span class="regexp">/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Linux </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Scala常用于语法</title>
      <link href="/2018/11/01/scala%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>/2018/11/01/scala%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="高阶函数带泛型"><a href="#高阶函数带泛型" class="headerlink" title="高阶函数带泛型"></a>高阶函数带泛型</h1><figure class="highlight scala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">object</span> <span class="title">WordCount</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">parseplan</span></span>(sql:<span class="type">String</span>):<span class="type">List</span>\[<span class="type">Int</span>\]=parse(sql)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        im=&gt;<span class="number">2</span>::<span class="number">1</span>::<span class="type">Nil</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!--more--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">parse</span> </span>[<span class="type">T</span>](command:<span class="type">String</span>)(toresult:<span class="type">String</span>=&gt;<span class="type">T</span>):<span class="type">T</span>=&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        toresult(command)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">main</span></span>(args: <span class="type">Array</span>\[<span class="type">String</span>\]): <span class="type">Unit</span> = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">       println(parseplan(<span class="string">"c"</span>))</span><br><span class="line">   &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><h1 id="隐士参数注入"><a href="#隐士参数注入" class="headerlink" title="隐士参数注入"></a>隐士参数注入</h1><figure class="highlight scala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">implicit</span> <span class="keyword">var</span> a=<span class="string">"b"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">imFunction</span></span>(<span class="keyword">implicit</span> input:<span class="type">String</span>)=&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    print(input)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">main</span></span>(args: <span class="type">Array</span>\[<span class="type">String</span>\]): <span class="type">Unit</span> = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    imFunction</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>#隐式函数转换</p><figure class="highlight scala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">implicit</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">toInt1</span></span>(a:<span class="type">Double</span>):<span class="type">Int</span>=&#123;</span><br><span class="line">a.toInt</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">main</span></span>(args: <span class="type">Array</span>\[<span class="type">String</span>\]): <span class="type">Unit</span> = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">val</span> temp:<span class="type">Int</span>=<span class="number">3.0</span></span><br><span class="line">    print(temp)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="隐式类转换"><a href="#隐式类转换" class="headerlink" title="隐式类转换"></a>隐式类转换</h1><figure class="highlight scala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">implicit</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">ImClass</span>(<span class="params">x:<span class="type">Class</span></span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">sayhi=print</span></span>(x.member)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Class</span>(<span class="params">var member:<span class="type">String</span></span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="title">def</span> <span class="title">main</span>(<span class="params">args: <span class="type">Array</span>\[<span class="type">String</span>\]</span>)</span>: <span class="type">Unit</span> = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="type">Class</span>(<span class="string">"ni"</span>).sayhi</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="辅助构造器"><a href="#辅助构造器" class="headerlink" title="辅助构造器"></a>辅助构造器</h1><figure class="highlight scala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">auxConstructor</span>(<span class="params">var member1:<span class="type">String</span>,var member2:<span class="type">String</span></span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    self=&gt; <span class="comment">//相当于this</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> name:<span class="type">String</span>=_</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">this</span></span>(<span class="type">Input</span>:<span class="type">String</span>,member3:<span class="type">String</span>,member4:<span class="type">String</span>) &#123; <span class="comment">//辅助构造器</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">this</span>(member3,member4)</span><br><span class="line">        self.name=<span class="type">Input</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">object</span> <span class="title">WordCount</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">main</span></span>(args: <span class="type">Array</span>\[<span class="type">String</span>\]): <span class="type">Unit</span> = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        println(<span class="keyword">new</span> auxConstructor(<span class="string">"1"</span>, <span class="string">"2"</span>, <span class="string">"3"</span>).name)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="函数定义方式"><a href="#函数定义方式" class="headerlink" title="函数定义方式"></a>函数定义方式</h1><figure class="highlight scala"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">a=3</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="title">def</span> <span class="title">b</span></span>()=<span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">c</span></span>(m1:<span class="type">Int</span>)=&#123;<span class="number">3</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">e=</span></span>(m1:<span class="type">Int</span>)=&gt;<span class="number">3</span> <span class="comment">//e为函数</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Linux </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
  
  
